	* [r952] src/FTPixmapGlyph.cpp, src/FTTextureGlyph.cpp:
	  * Align FTPixmapGlyph and FTTextureGlyph objects at round pixel
	  coordinates
	  to reduce bleeding. Patch by Ton Roosendaal, from Blender commit
	  r4411.

